{"id":10999,"date":"2024-03-17T16:12:14","date_gmt":"2024-03-17T09:12:14","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/?p=10999"},"modified":"2024-03-17T16:20:09","modified_gmt":"2024-03-17T09:20:09","slug":"nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi\/","title":{"rendered":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec?"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ng\u00e0y nay, vi\u1ec7c\u00a0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ecdn Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0m n\u01a1i sinh s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c l\u00e2u d\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u hi\u1ebfm g\u1eb7p. V\u00ec x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u201can c\u01b0 l\u1ea1c nghi\u1ec7p\u201d n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y n\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh mua cho m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t c\u0103n nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec7n cho vi\u1ec7c sinh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. V\u1eady <\/span><b>ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ecba kh\u00f4ng? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/vinhomeland.com.vn\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vinhomeland<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi n\u00e0y \u1edf b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft sau \u0111\u00e2y nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>6 \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1ec1 quy \u0111\u1ecbnh mua nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u00e0nh cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i.<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mua v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_11001\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11001\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11001 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi.jpg\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11001\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11001\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi.jpg\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-11001\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, Nh\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1eabn cho ph\u00e9p vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, nh\u01b0ng \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c s\u1edf h\u1eefu, h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n kh\u1eaft khe, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c; \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u1ea1i qu\u1ed1c s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u1ea5t \u00edt. Tuy nhi\u00ean, 5 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Lu\u1eadt nh\u00e0 \u1edf \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed5i, n\u1edbi l\u1ecfng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, v\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i sinh s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y t\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>M\u1edf r\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u00e0nh cho kh\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i.<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_11002\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11002\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11002 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi-1.jpg\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11002\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11002\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi-1.jpg\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-11002\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">M\u1edf r\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u1ea1i qu\u1ed1c<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Nh\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho \u0111a d\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ngo\u1ea1i qu\u1ed1c, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng nh\u00e0 \u1edf theo d\u1ef1 \u00e1n t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f3 v\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i, chi nh\u00e1nh ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p ph\u00e9p nh\u1eadp c\u1ea3nh v\u00e0o Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00f4ng qua c\u00e1c h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c sau \u0111\u00e2y:<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_11003\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11003\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11003 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi-2.jpg\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11003\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11003\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi-2.jpg\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-11003\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1c h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c mua nh\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i<\/p><\/div>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng nh\u00e0 \u1edf theo d\u1ef1 \u00e1n t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Mua, thu\u00ea, nh\u1eadn th\u1eeba k\u1ebf nh\u00e0 \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i bao g\u1ed3m nh\u00e0 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t ho\u1eb7c chung c\u01b0 trong d\u1ef1 \u00e1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng nh\u00e0 \u1edf ( tr\u1eeb khu v\u1ef1c thu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea1m vi qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1)<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf c\u1ee7a c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_11004\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11004\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11004 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi-3.jpg\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11004\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11004\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi-3.jpg\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-11004\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i \u00edt h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">&#8211; \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi chung c\u01b0:<\/span><\/h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mua, thu\u00ea, nh\u1eadn th\u1eeba k\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 30% s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0103n h\u1ed9 trong m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 d\u00e2n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng khu v\u1ef1c h\u00e0nh ch\u00ednh c\u1ea5p ph\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u to\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 th\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u1ea1i qu\u1ed1c ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ed1i \u0111a 30% s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng chung c\u01b0 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i to\u00e0 nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 30% t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 c\u0103n h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c to\u00e0 chung c\u01b0 n\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">&#8211; \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 \u1edf ri\u00eang l\u1ebb:<\/span><\/h4>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 khu v\u1ef1c c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 d\u00e2n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb h\u00e0nh ch\u00ednh c\u1ea5p ph\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u00e1n x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1edbi 2500 c\u0103n:<\/strong> Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u1ea1i qu\u1ed1c ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a 10% t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u00e0 trong d\u1ef1 \u00e1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u00e1n nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t 2500 c\u0103n:<\/strong> Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u1ea1i qu\u1ed1c ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a 250 c\u0103n trong d\u1ef1 \u00e1n \u0111\u00f3.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_11005\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11005\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11005 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi-4.jpg\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11005\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11005\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi-4.jpg\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-11005\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p ph\u00e9p s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 theo giao d\u1ecbch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua b\u00e1n, thu\u00ea, nh\u1eadn th\u1eeba k\u1ebf trong v\u00f2ng 50 n\u0103m k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>Gia h\u1ea1n:<\/strong> Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n th\u1eddi gian s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n n\u00e0y th\u00ec ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c gia h\u1ea1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3 th\u00e1ng. Gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd bao g\u1ed3m: \u0111\u01a1n xin \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n, b\u1ea3n sao Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf; hai lo\u1ea1i gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed9p \u1edf U\u1ef7 ban nh\u00e2n d\u00e2n c\u1ea5p t\u1ec9nh n\u01a1i c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f3. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p gia h\u1ea1n 1 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 50 n\u0103m.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i k\u1ebft h\u00f4n v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u1eb7c k\u1ebft h\u00f4n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i th\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng quy\u1ec1n v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u00f4ng d\u00e2n Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>Khi h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu:<\/strong> C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n b\u00e1n, t\u1eb7ng ho\u1eb7c cho. N\u1ebfu c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nhu c\u1ea7u tr\u00ean th\u00ec b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n n\u00e0y thu\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i cho thu\u00ea nh\u00e0 \u1edf t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed9p thu\u1ebf<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_11006\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11006\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11006 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi-5.jpg\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11006\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11006\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi-5.jpg\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-11006\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i cho thu\u00ea nh\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed9p thu\u1ebf<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">N\u1ebfu c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch cho thu\u00ea (\u0111\u00fang v\u1edbi quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt) th\u00ec ph\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi c\u01a1 quan qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea5t c\u1ea5p huy\u1ec7n, ph\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh n\u1ed9p thu\u1ebf.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i (Vi\u1ec7t Ki\u1ec1u), t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam bao g\u1ed3m c\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p 1<\/b><b>: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mua nh\u00e0 \u1edf t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_11007\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11007\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11007 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi-6.jpg\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11007\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11007\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi-6.jpg\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-11007\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/p><\/div>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng sinh s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i ( Theo K3, \u0110i\u1ec1u 3 Lu\u1eadt QT 2008)<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ed1c Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u01b0ng khi sinh ra qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh theo nguy\u00ean t\u1eafc huy\u1ebft th\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 con, ch\u00e1u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111ang c\u01b0 tr\u00fa v\u00e0 sinh s\u1ed1ng l\u00e2u d\u00e0i \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i ( K4 \u0110i\u1ec1u 3 LQT 2008).<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p ph\u00e9p nh\u1eadp c\u1ea3nh v\u00e0o Vi\u1ec7t Nam, th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c bao g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd ch\u1ee9ng minh nh\u01b0 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng mang h\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00ec ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f3ng d\u1ea5u ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 quan qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd xu\u1ea5t, nh\u1eadp c\u1ea3nh Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o h\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu v\u00e0 h\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i c\u00f2n h\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">N\u1ebfu mang h\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i th\u00ec h\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i c\u00f2n gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00f3ng d\u1ea5u b\u1edfi c\u01a1 quan qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd xu\u1ea5t nh\u1eadp c\u1ea3nh Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o h\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu. Ngo\u00e0i ra c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd ch\u1ee9ng minh m\u00ecnh mang qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch Vi\u1ec7t Nam ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd x\u00e1c minh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ed1c Vi\u1ec7t do S\u1edf T\u01b0 ph\u00e1p c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c t\u1ec9nh, th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 tr\u1ef1c thu\u1ed9c trung \u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea5p.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p 2<\/b><b>: Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i<\/b><\/span><\/h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_11008\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11008\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11008 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi-7.jpg\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11008\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11008\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi-7.jpg\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-11008\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i<\/p><\/div>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i bao g\u1ed3m: Doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f3 v\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i, c\u00e1c ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c c\u00f3 chi nh\u00e1nh t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, c\u00e1c doanh nghi\u1ec7p n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i nh\u01b0ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u1eefng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 quan nh\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f3 th\u1ea9m quy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea5p gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 th\u00ec m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p ph\u00e9p nh\u1eadp c\u1ea3nh ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 quy\u1ec1n \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i hay mi\u1ec5n tr\u1eeb ngo\u1ea1i giao n\u00e0o.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i khi mua c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u00ec th\u00f4ng qua h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c g\u00ec?<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<div id=\"attachment_11009\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11009\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11009 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi-8.jpg\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11009\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11009\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi-8.jpg\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-11009\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1c h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c mua nh\u00e0<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt trong \u0111i\u1ec3m b, kho\u1ea3n 2 \u0110i\u1ec1u 8 Lu\u1eadt nh\u00e0 \u1edf 2014:<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i th\u00ec th\u00f4ng qua h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p kinh doanh b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n; nh\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5t \u1edf trong d\u1ef1 \u00e1n \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p b\u00e1n n\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng nh\u00e0 \u1edf.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, theo kho\u1ea3n 1, \u0110i\u1ec1u 75, N\u011099\/2015 quy \u0111\u1ecbnh:<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1edf h\u1eefu 2 lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n sau: c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u1edf ri\u00eang l\u1ebb ( tr\u1eeb b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u1ea3n \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c qu\u1ed1c ph\u00f2ng, qu\u00e2n s\u1ef1)<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>Th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c c\u1ea5p ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<div id=\"attachment_11010\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11010\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11010 lazyload\" data-src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi-9.jpg\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" src=\"data:image\/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" style=\"--smush-placeholder-width: 800px; --smush-placeholder-aspect-ratio: 800\/450;\" \/><noscript><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11010\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11010\" src=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi-9.jpg\" alt=\"ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" \/><\/noscript><p id=\"caption-attachment-11010\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c c\u1ea5p gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i<\/p><\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">C\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u mua nh\u00e0 \u1edf t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">\u0110\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ea5p gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00e0 quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5t ( c\u1ea3 b\u1ea3n Ti\u1ebfng Anh v\u00e0 Ti\u1ebfng Vi\u1ec7t)<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd v\u1ec1 quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf c\u1ee7a b\u00ean b\u00e1n<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">&#8211; Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p mua c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0:\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u00ea duy\u1ec7t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n nh\u00e0 \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u01a1 quan c\u00f3 th\u1ea9m quy\u1ec1n<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho thu\u00ea ho\u1eb7c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh giao \u0111\u1ea5t<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Bi\u00ean b\u1ea3n b\u00e0n giao c\u0103n h\u1ed9\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">S\u1edf \u0111\u1ed3 m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng c\u0103n h\u1ed9\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">&#8211; Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p mua, nh\u1eadn th\u1eeba k\u1ebf c\u0103n h\u1ed9 chung c\u01b0 trong c\u00e1c d\u1ef1 \u00e1n nh\u00e0 \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify; list-style-type: circle;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ec1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u00e0 \u1edf v\u00e0 quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5t<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn quy\u1ec1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea5t c\u00f3 ghi nh\u1eadn nh\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mua b\u00e1n, th\u1eeba k\u1ebf nh\u00e0 \u1edf<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">B\u1ea3n sao ch\u1ee9ng th\u1ef1c h\u1ed9 chi\u1ebfu n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i v\u00e0 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Gi\u1ea5y x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn giao d\u1ecbch khi mua c\u0103n h\u1ed9 theo \u0111\u00fang quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px;\">Bi\u00ean lai n\u1ed9p thu\u1ebf, l\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vinhomeland<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> \u0111\u00e3 cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng tin c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u201c<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/www.vinhomeland.com.vn\/nguoi-nuoc-ngoai-mua-nha-can-giay-to-gi\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><b>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i mua nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7n gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd g\u00ec<\/b><\/a><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">?\u201d. Hy v\u1ecdng qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ed9c gi\u1ea3 s\u1ebd t\u00edch l\u0169y th\u00eam cho m\u0